	     <table class="mform"  border="0" cellpadding="1" cellspacing="0" width="100%" >
	     <form action="/cgi-bin/mrate.pl" name="f98312849217302">
	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="/search.shtml?faction=181&amp;mid=98312849217302">How I raised faction wizzy style</a> <a id="fs8" href="/search.shtml?faction=181&amp;mid=98312849217302#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Sun, Feb 25th 2:14 PM 2001</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br /><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Good [4.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Okay here it is.&nbsp;&nbsp;The note was nerfed but you can raise faction.  I was apprehensive to start. Here's what I did.<br/><br/>1.  Took boat to OOT went to gornit island bound myself at loc. p680 n5325.<br/><br/>2.  Set up the following hot keys.  I numbered mine 1-4 just to make things easier.<br/>    1. /say yes<br/>    2. /say he threatened my life<br/>    3. /say who are you<br/>    4. /say I wish to know more<br/>note: if you are indiff or above you don't need the hot keys but it makes it easier.<br/><br/>3.  Killed Capt Surestout after pulling him to my bindpoint.  He is the tent. lesser spirit spawns.<br/><br/>4. Hail lesser spirit.  Keep him targeted while you sit and camp. hailing him every few seconds till camped out.<br/><br/>5. Log back in!  hail lesser spirit then hit the hot keys in order.  you have approx 15 seconds to complete this since your faction is at indiff till then.  You should get a gem from the lesser spirit.<br/><br/>6.  Gate to N Ro.  run to N Freeport to the NW corner of the zone. (near the building where they sell muffins)  Jump in water swim through tunnel a short distance you will see a breeak in the wall with an NPC named Bondl Felligan.  You are going to want to camp and log back in again if you are apprehensive or lower.  Yeah its a pain but it works.<br/><br/>7. Hail Bondl.  Then hand him the Gem.<br/>   Your faction with TrueSpirit got better<br/>   You gain party experience.<br/><br/>8. Gate to bind point repeat.  Lesser may still be up for a couple of trips.<br/><br/>Final notes.  I had to to the camping trick 3 times if I remember right to get to indiff.  Then you can do the quest without camping and the gating to bind point helps alot because of downtime that would be caused by the boat ride.<br/><br/>Good Luck to you all<br/><br/>&lt;name withheld&gt;<br/>to protect the innocent<br/></p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
